Rooms.Policy:
Enjoy a convenient breakfast at the property for COP 10,000 per person, per night. Children and Extra Bed Policy: Children cannot be accommodated at the hotel. There is no capacity for extra beds in the room.  Deposit Policy: No deposit will be charged.  Cancellation Policy: If canceled or modified up to 1 day before the date of arrival,  no fee will be charged. If canceled or modified later or in case of no-show, 100 percent of the first night will be charged. 

Meal Plan: Enjoy a convenient breakfast at the property for COP 10,000 per person, per night.
